{"id":2024,"date":"2012-02-29T09:20:04","date_gmt":"2012-02-29T14:20:04","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=2024"},"modified":"2023-03-23T17:04:38","modified_gmt":"2023-03-23T13:04:38","slug":"mindful-allah-he-will-protect-you","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/29\/mindful-allah-he-will-protect-you\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Qadr: Be mindful of Allah, He will protect you"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ibn Abbas reported: I was riding behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when he said to me, \u201c<strong>Young man, I will teach you some words. Be mindful of Allah and He will protect you. Be mindful of Allah and you will find Him before you. If you ask, ask from Allah. If you seek help, seek help from Allah. Know that if the nations gathered together to benefit you, they could not benefit you unless Allah has decreed it for you. And if the nations gathered together to harm you, they could not harm you unless Allah has decreed it for you. The pens have been lifted and the pages have dried<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2516<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Sahih\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064f \u062e\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u063a\u064f\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0644